As said before and *numerous* times thought the ages...Concussion works even when resisted, same with Jolt and the like.  And if I remember correctly on Emperor you use cold damage.  Even just using say Draught of E`ci you can *easily* do more damage rather than just wasting a full manabar.  It's not free damage, it does limited damage all in one shot and then it takes you out of the action.  Aggro bound...lord go back to AoW and learn how to nuke from 98% and keep going the whole fight without being summoned and yet outdamaging every other class there besides maybe rogues and necros.  Manaburn is just a cop out, an excuse for the lazy or those that don't know how to control your aggro. <br>
