Next time you fight the emp try counting to 7 between nukes, you'll find it'll have the same effect as casting concussion. (I have A:GC, have tested it a bunch, and I don't see any reason to believe concussion works when resisted. See above reasoning in first paragraph for explaination.) <p><!--EZCODE LINK START--><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=10932" target="top"><!--EZCODE IMAGE START--><img src="http://members.rogers.com/maxwellg/khael2.jpg" style="border:0;"/><!--EZCODE IMAGE END--></a><!--EZCODE LINK END--><br>
